SpeechKit framework is a high-level framework. --> speech recognizer, and text to speech
1. audio component, manage for recording 
2. networking component --> manage network
3. end-of-speech detector ---> when user stop speaking, and automatically stops recording.
4. encoding component --> streaming audio's compression.

Speech kit follows a server-based architecture
voice recognition --> SKRecognizer
convert text to speech ----> SKVocalizer. 

  
